def test_all_methods(self, invoke):
        output = invoke(["routes"]).output
        assert "GET, HEAD, OPTIONS, POST" not in output
        output = invoke(["routes", "--all-methods"]).output
        assert "GET, HEAD, OPTIONS, POST" in output
